- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a likely category as the paper discusses the construction of logical operations in a cellular automaton, which involves manipulating data structures and algorithms.
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another likely category as the Game of Life is a type of artificial life simulation, and the paper discusses the evolution of patterns and gliders in the automaton.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses the implementation of logical functions, which is a fundamental concept in AI.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the Game of Life can be seen as a type of control system, and the paper discusses the construction of logical operations in this system.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper discusses the decomposition of Boolean functions, which is a concept relevant to programming languages.
